gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Celtics 124, Bulls 97
gameRecap.excerpt: The Celtics defeated the Bulls, 124-97, and improve to 14-4 on the year and 3-1 in East C play. The Bulls move to 5-14 on the year and 0-4 in East C play.
